#id=1
#text=When I baked a cake , I got my dishes out from the cupboard in my kitchen .
#id=2
#text=I laid out all the dishes and ingredients needed to bake my cake .
#id=3
#text=After preheating the dishes and preheating the oven to a set temperature , I started on making my frosting .
#id=4
#text=I broke the eggs and separated the yolks and the whites , and I set up my flour in my pans .
#id=5
#text=I then went on to making and mixing my frosting and my batter in their respective bowls .
#id=6
#text=The batter was finished and then placed into the baking pan for about the next half hour .
#id=7
#text=After the oven timer went off , I checked on the way the batter had risen and settled , and found that my cake was ready to be decorated with the frosting .
#id=8
#text=This was meant to be a birthday cake , so I bought festive frosting add-ons to go with my original homemade frosting .
#id=9
#text=I applied the homemade frosting to the cake first , then squirted the store-bought frosting onto the cake through the funnel .
#text=I wrote several words on the cake as well to make it more personalized for the person whom the birthday was happening for .
#text=I also set aside several candles for the birthday boy to blow out later on .
